CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 4, 1960, pg. A8 reads:"YMCA Marks 50th Anniversary - Centre Avenue YMCA celebrated its 50th anniversary on May 29 with a program at Warren Methodist Church. Above, left to right; B.H. Logan, chairman, Christian education committee; the Rev. William J. Harvey III, pastor, Macedonia Baptist Church; Atty. Byrd Brown, chairman, committee of management; Bishop Joseph Gomez, principal speaker; the Rev. Ramsey Bridges, member of committee and host pastor, and James M. Burgett, executive secretary, Centre Avenue YMCA. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Man wearing suit, shaking hands with Bishop Joseph Gomez, standing at altar railing with group of men and women waiting in line, in Warren Methodist Church for Centre Avenue YMCA fiftieth anniversary
